title: 1-Bedroom Available at Grande Market Place
posting_body: ["Grande Market Place Apartments are located in the center of the city with convenient access to shopping, transportation, schools, entertainment, 35W, and 35E. The community offers 113 apartments with large studio, 1 & 2 bedroom apartment homes for today's diverse lifestyles.", 'Amenities include an in-unit washer/dryer, balcony, fitness center, updated vinyl plank flooring in most units, and more.', '1 bedroom | 1 bath | 913-929 sq ft. | Starting at $862/month', '**Photos were taken in a similar model; layouts, finishes, and view may vary.', 'For more information call :', 'show contact info', 'Building Amenities:', '*Walk-In Closets', 'Washer/Dryer in Unit', 'Breakfast Bar', 'Dishwasher', '*Patio/Balcony', 'Carpet and Vinyl Flooring', 'Individual Climate Control', 'High Speed Internet Available', '10 Channel Satellite TV', 'Water, Sewer, Trash Included', '*In Select Units', 'Community Amenities:', 'Located in the "Heart of The City"', '24-hour Fitness Center', 'Community Room', 'Courtyard', 'Underground Parking Available $50/month | Free Street Parking | City Ramp Availability', 'Cats Welcome (with $300 non-refundable fee | Restrictions Apply)', 'Central Air Conditioning', '24 Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Controlled Access Entry', 'Great Nearby Parks & Shopping', 'Close Proximity with the Burnsville Transit Center', '*Rents subject to change daily, please contact us for the most updated pricing', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY']
